data.text:
Consumer Contact Numbers

See this consumer KanCare Contact List for information and phone numbers to get your questions answered. Not sure who to call?Who Should I Call - Consumers

KanCare Ombudsman Office (855-643-8180)

1-855-643-8180

Relay: 711

Kancare.ombudsman@ks.gov

www.KanCareOmbudsman.ks.gov

Do you have questions about Kansas Medicaid or KanCare? Need help?

Kansas Medicaid, known as KanCare, can be hard to understand. The KanCare Ombudsman office can help with:

Answers to questions

Resolving issues

Understanding letters from KanCare

Responding when you disagree with a decision or change

Completing an application or renewal

Filing a complaint (grievance)

Filing an appeal or fair hearing

Learning about in-home services also called Home and Community Based Services (HCBS)
